                     </persName>
                      
                   the elder, and thereby did transfer 50 l. part of 450 l. of joint stock of South Sea Annuities. the property of the said 
                     <persName id="t17680907-72-person716">
                        Richard
                     <interp inst="t17680907-72-person716" type="given" value="Richard"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t17680907-72-person716" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
